      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  F U N C T I O N   O F   I N D I C A T O R S                  *
      *                                                               *
      *   89  - Work indicator for Chain/Read operations              *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      /SPACE 3
     E                    CPY@    1   1 80
      *
      ** Array containing Copyright statement
      *
      /EJECT
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           PRTCD   7
     C                     PARM           PMODE   1
      *
      ** Copyright statement
      *
     C                     MOVEACPY@      CPY@@   1
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   PRTCD
      *
      ** Initialisation processing
      *
     C           PMODE     IFEQ '1'
     C           PMODE     OREQ '2'
      *
     C                     READ SDGELRPD                 89
      *
     C           *IN89     IFEQ *OFF
      *
     C                     MOVE *ZEROS    BKNDFV
     C                     MOVE 'N'       BKAFVN
     C                     MOVE 'N'       BKAFVD
     C                     MOVE 'N'       BKAFVC
     C                     MOVE 'N'       BKAFVG
      *
     C                     UPDATSDGELRD0
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ** If MODE = '3', set new fields to blank.
      *
     C           PMODE     IFEQ '3'
      *
     C                     READ SDGELRPD                 89
      *
     C           *IN89     IFEQ *OFF
      *
     C                     MOVE *ZEROS    BKNDFV
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    BKAFVN
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    BKAFVD
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    BKAFVC
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    BKAFVG
      *
     C                     UPDATSDGELRD0
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE '1'       *INLR
      *
